1
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:12,760
Yuan.

2
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,080
Actually,

3
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,420
I've always wanted to ask you something.

4
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,039
You...

5
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,680
Do you hate humans?

6
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:26,280
I do.

7
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:28,320
Why?

8
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,640
Yuan,

9
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,120
can you tell me?

10
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:36,810
This is really important to me.

11
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,160
It's too dangerous for you here.

12
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,690
I'll get you out of here now.

13
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,600
I don't care how you found me.

14
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,940
Don't come looking for me ever again.

15
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:13,960
Then tell me

16
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,360
why you hate the human race so much,

17
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,620
and I won't come looking for you anymore.

18
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,040
What exactly do you want?

19
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,890
I want to resolve

20
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:26,160
your grudge against the human race.

21
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,280
Don't think I won't kill you.

22
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,490
Grandma,

23
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:36,079
please get up.

24
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,079
Grandma.

25
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,340
Hurry and save her!

26
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,040
Hurry!

27
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,200
Don't forget,

28
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,480
I am a man-eating demon.

29
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,320
You are not.

30
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,200
Don't be afraid, baby.

31
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,000
Grandma is here.

32
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,720
Grandma.

33
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:20,920
I knew

34
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,320
you wouldn't leave us to die.

35
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:22,960
Get up.

36
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,680
Thank you.

37
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,160
Thank you.

38
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,220
No need to thank me.

39
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,600
I just took pity on you for being old, weak, sick, and disabled.

40
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,240
I can understand "old and weak."

41
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,760
But what do you mean by "sick and disabled"?

42
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,360
Danyu.

43
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:35,680
Danyu.

44
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,090
Let's go.

45
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,840
Danyu.

46
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,640
Danyu,

47
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,050
why are you here?

48
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:44,960
Lan.

49
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,079
Why are you two together?

50
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,200
So,

51
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,680
you went to the Netherworld to find him?

52
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,000
Huh?

53
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:05,620
You actually went to the Netherworld alone for him?

54
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,000
Brother Wuzhou.

55
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:11,890
Previously,

56
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,440
didn't she also sleep in the Demon Lord's room?

57
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,520
That wasn't...

58
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,880
Lu Danyu.

59
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,250
Do you know that you are a human?

60
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,120
No matter how much you like him,

61
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,440
you shouldn't have run

62
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,560
to the demon headquarters,

63
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,920
walking right into the lion's den.

64
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,250
What were you thinking?

65
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,920
If anything happened to you,

66
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,960
how could I live?

67
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,600
I was wrong.

68
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:37,640
Okay,

69
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:38,620
step aside.

70
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,490
I'll go find Lan.

71
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:41,520
I...

72
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,409
I'm going to find him

73
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,540
to have a few words.

74
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,980
I'll go help the auntie fetch some water.

75
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,420
Demon Lord.

76
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,880
My sister is young and ignorant.

77
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,040
Thank you, Demon Lord, for taking good care of her.

78
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,240
I didn't do anything.

79
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,820
Let alone take care of her.

80
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,940
No need to thank me.

81
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:03,930
Alright.

82
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,880
Then let's talk about

83
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,850
the relationship between you two.

84
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,360
What?

85
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,600
What kind of luck is this?

86
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:22,040
How did we bump into them as soon as we came out?

87
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:25,440
It might be the connection between me and the Child of the World.

88
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,000
True.

89
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,810
This probably can't even be considered mysticism anymore.

90
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,480
Alright.

91
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,120
What should we do now?

92
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,640
Ayuan won't say anything even with me pestering him.

93
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,840
Now that Mu Chenxue and Wei Wuzhou are here,

94
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,360
I guess

95
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:39,170
he's even less likely to speak.

96
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,560
I think

97
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,960
you should first figure out

98
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:45,220
how to get past Wei Wuzhou and Mu Chenxue.

99
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:50,159
There is no way I can clear my name now.

100
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,370
I have no romantic issues with her.

101
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,140
Demon Lord,

102
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,520
even if you are a demon,

103
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,280
you can't just abandon her after taking advantage of her.

104
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:02,810
Exactly.

105
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,220
You slept together at the inn before.

106
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:06,160
And now, for your sake,

107
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,600
she even ran to the Netherworld.

108
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,600
Her love for you is

109
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,360
so deep.

110
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:12,360
How can you say you have no romantic issues?

111
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:12,840
I...

112
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,360
Things are not what you think.

113
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,640
We didn't imagine anything.

114
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,080
What we are saying now

115
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:22,080
is what we saw with our own eyes.

116
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:22,760
Right.

117
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:23,840
With our own eyes.

118
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,410
Seeing is not necessarily believing.

119
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,080
There is really nothing between me and her.

120
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,560
Nowadays,

121
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,560
even a demon will deny it.

122
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,080
Poor Lu Danyu,

123
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,000
her sincere heart

124
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,320
is going down the drain.

125
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,120
Sure enough,

126
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:42,540
a girl just shouldn't fall in love first.

127
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,840
I can't explain it clearly to you in a few words.

128
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,170
If you don't believe me,

129
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,159
just confront her directly.

130
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:49,960
You are right.

131
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:50,720
Let's go.

132
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,880
We will confront them later.

133
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,600
After the confrontation,

134
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,600
the responsibility

135
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,400
must be taken.

136
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,600
Danyu!

137
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,840
Danyu!

138
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,080
Danyu!

139
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,690
Does fetching water take so...

140
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,280
This kind of spiritual power...

141
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,690
Tiandao Palace.

142
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:20,450
Tiandao Palace?

143
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,220
Demon Lord.

144
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,600
Do you mean

145
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,000
Danyu was captured by the Tiandao Palace?

146
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,560
What?

147
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,400
Yiyi.

148
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,250
Why do I still have a part like this?

149
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,480
It is inevitable that Tiandao Palace

150
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,600
brings back the pure-blooded Likong.

151
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,730
Their clan has always lived deep within Tiandao Palace.

152
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,600
Then what should we do now?

153
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,680
If the Son and Daughter of the World find out you are missing,

154
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:04,680
they will probably come looking for you immediately.

155
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,880
Then,

156
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:10,090
do you think Lanqi Moyuan will come to save me?

157
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,340
Palace Master,

158
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,730
the strayed Likong clan member

159
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,020
has been brought back.

160
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,720
The Likong clan

161
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:43,400
has always been the hero of our human race in suppressing the Netherworld.

162
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:44,560
I presume she

163
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,800
will also become one of them.

164
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,640
To sacrifice for the human race

165
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,800
is their honor.

166
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,400
Senior Brother.

167
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,520
How is the girl inside

168
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,360
doing now?

169
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:05,880
Reporting to Senior Brother.

170
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,680
She is very quiet

171
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:07,740
and well-behaved.

172
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,040
Open the door.
